flowchart TD
  A["Is annual electricity enough?"] --> B["Is firm capacity enough at summer peak?"]
  B --> C["Is evening / night capacity enough after solar falls?"]
  C --> D["Is operating reserve margin adequate during heat waves?"]
  D --> E["Is clean power available for corporate demand?"]
  E --> F["Can the grid deliver power to fabs and data centers?"]
  F --> G["Can the system absorb fuel, outage, and weather shocks?"]
  G --> H["Power adequacy status: easing, stable, worsening, or unclear"]
